To follow in Sarah Jessica Parker’s footsteps, we suggest brushing out your tresses after adding a volumizing mousse to your roots for ultimate frizz. For a bit more dimension, add a lightweight leave-in conditioner and detangling serum before combing through.

description: Lightweight products are essential when it comes to doing your hair, especially with tight curls. It doesn’t take much to bring out your frizz, but avoiding creams and serums that weigh your coils down is key when adding that extra umph. Shop curl enhancing shampoos and conditioners, stimulating scalp massagers, curl crème, and more.

description: Charlize Theron has sustained a career in Hollywood for nearly 30 years because she still loves it and wants it to be better. (And because her kids are watching too.) “There’s a natural fight in me to want to create environments that feel like the things that I wish I had 30 years ago when I started,” she tells @leahchernikoff. In our October 22 cover story the actress, producer, and philanthropist opens up about motherhood—and making movies on her own terms.
